        <abstract>
            <p>Coloration of butterflies; brilliantly coloured females.</p> 
<p>Commends CD on his paper on specific differences in <hi rend="italic">Primula</hi> [<hi rend="italic">J. Proc. Linn. Soc. Lond. (Bot.)</hi> 10 (1869): 437–54; reprinted and revised in <hi rend="italic">Forms of flowers</hi>] as a test-case proving origin of real species.</p> 
